# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#599, stdlib’s pipenv should not be VCSed.
#   Pipfile.lock is exception.
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock is database and should be tracked.
#poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, pdm.lock is database and should be tracked.
#.pdm-python
